    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concluded that the seven assessed factors, taken together, provide sufficient evidence to support the hemolysis prediction claim at Model Risk Level 3. The three unassessed factors — numerical solver error, use error, and model form — were considered beyond the scope of the current submission phase and were not expected to materially affect the overall credibility conclusion. No concrete alternative mitigations were identified for these gaps. The decision to accept reflects the team's judgment that the assessed evidence is adequate, notwithstanding the uncharacterized epistemic gaps at MRL 3.",
